						 <p>This is a draft that's been in the works for a long while. And by in the works for a long while I mean I got lazy with revising it and didn't make changes in almost a full year.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562106566" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" >Weryllium</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562106566" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span> for crit on the original version of this, and to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4483018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562106566" alt="TheMightyMcB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4483018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" >TheMightyMcB</a></span> for looking this version over before I boldposted. If I'm missing anyone do let me know!</p> <p>For more of the Toronto Demon Council, check out:</p> <ul> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/post-post-mortem-delights">Post-Post-Mortem Delights</a> (minor role but they're there)</li> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/cease-and-deceased">Cease and Deceased</a></li> </ul> <p>(note that 4631 isn't in the same storyline as these articles. it is in the same setting, though.)</p> <p>EDIT: Stupidly forgot to include image attribution but <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c-dives" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2375337&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562106566" alt="C-Dives" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2375337)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c-dives" >C-Dives</a></span> has that covered. Thanks!</p> 
